    <p>Fear of own­ing HSBC Hold­ings shares is turn­ing into a fear of miss­ing out on a ma­jor rally.</p>
    <p>Europe’s big­gest lender is up 55 per cent in Hong Kong af­ter touch­ing its 25-year low in Septem­ber, and is the best-per­form­ing stock on the Hang Seng In­dex this quar­ter.</p>
    <p>Just two months ago, in­vestors were fret­ting over how mount­ing reg­u­la­tory and eco­nomic pres­sures would squeeze the firm’s key busi­nesses in Asia.</p>

